Function: alpow
Section: algebras
C-Name: alpow
Prototype: GGG
Help: alpow(al,x,n): element x^n in al.
Doc: Given an element $x$ in \var{al} and an integer $n$, computes the
 power $x^n$ in the algebra \var{al}.
 \bprog
 ? A = alinit(nfinit(y), [-1,-1]);
 ? alpow(A,[1,1,0,0]~,7)
 %2 = [8, -8, 0, 0]~
 @eprog
